#First let's clean up the DF: Replace two Spaces with one Space
from pyspark.sql.functions import regexp_replace, col,count, expr, sum,split, explode, trim,size, concat,lit
df3= df2.withColumn("splitted1",split(trim(col("Product"))," ").getItem(0))
df3 = df3.withColumn("splitted2",split(trim(col("Product"))," ").getItem(1))
df3 = df3.withColumn("Product1",concat(lit(col("splitted1")),lit(col("splitted2"))))
df4 = df3.groupBy("Product1").agg(count("Product1").alias("Total_complaints")).sort("Total_complaints",ascending=False).limit(10)
pdf4 = df4.toPandas()
pdf4.plot.bar(x='Product1', y='Total_complaints')
